{"tid":1400280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[護心] 皇天擊殺 心臟病發","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T18:12:07.000Z","uid":162215,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54215dfd0509cd76479d2eb162f9d07008b22b81","tid":1400280,"uid":162215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"『猝死』是在發病一個小時內突然心因性神智喪失造成死亡，猝死個案多半是青壯年男性。<br />\n需要注意的是，大部份的猝死來得突然，可能是在劇烈運動、精神壓力、情緒激躁、暴飲暴食、過度勞累、過冷過熱等情況下，突發死亡。<br />\n<br />\n以下人士病發機率較高:<br />\n飲食不規律，暴飲暴食者<br />\n長期菸酒過量的人<br />\n經常性熬夜，長期讓身心過度疲勞的人<br />\n經常叫霸王雞<br />\n生活習慣不定<br />\n<br />\n大家明點解要be water 要hit and run啦<br />\n犬隻三萬 人就係得咁多 周圍聚集佢就要OT<br />\n補水唔足 又唔夠訓 肯定好撚谷氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後上曬gear set曬場 班示威者又快閃走曬<br />\n精神壓力持續緊張 好易出事 <br />\n<br />\n重奪香港 八五罷工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46f108faab50e19af171b4e53c0b0e08954131f","tid":1400280,"uid":162215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"護心一推<br />\n聽日tko見"},{"pid":"122e54f24368cc7599a57d0b63c0dae4f98706a6","tid":1400280,"uid":162215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:11:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73c46bdfd597d342447e24e86c4ac6596bae5302","tid":1400280,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc0492374df0db7cb16fa98cff3fa4aa1648d796","tid":1400280,"uid":177047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"所以大家要養成良好生活習慣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfda0b4fcdd2c1a1bef628dd2f103ee0905cf3b2","tid":1400280,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa